<div id="pf561f" class="pf w43 h355" data-page-no="561f"><div class="pc pc561f w43 h355"><div class="t me31 x5d h11c y2f9c ff3 fs22 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the Principal Contributor of </div><div class="t maf3 xa h11c y2ca5 ff3 fs22 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This Quarter&apos;s Lessons </div><div class="t m114 x74 he yb7b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rosalie Haffner Lee trains and supervises Bible instructors in the Carolina </div><div class="t m41d x71 he ya14 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference. Working as a Bible instructor and a pastor&apos;s wife has been the focus </div><div class="t m577 x71 he y1554 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of her career. </div><div class="t m54e x74 he y9b8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee received her Bachelor of Arts degree from Union College, and </div><div class="t ma4 x71 he y16b7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">served as Bible instructor in California, Nebraska, and Michigan. She was an in-</div><div class="t m62b x71 he y1727 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">structor for the North American Division Evangelism Institute in Illinois before </div><div class="t m356 x16 he y1a4 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepting the position in the Carolina Conference. </div><div class="t m4c9 x74 he y189b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee has written a previous set of Sabbath School lessons, </div><div class="t me0a xe5 h35 y1b9d ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Songs of Ex-</div><div class="t m626 x16 h35 y1634 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perience, </div><div class="t m863 x53 he y108d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the Psalms, and authored a book entitled </div><div class="t m2fb xa7 h35 y5d6 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Let Me Tell You About My </div><div class="t ma1e x16 h35 y440 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. </div><div class="t m264 x4e he yd9b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In addition she has written for several Adventist publications. </div><div class="t m83e x74 he y514 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cooking, writing, and bird-watching occupy Mrs. Lee&apos;s leisure moments. Her </div><div class="t me1a x71 he ye67 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">husband, Kenneth, is a retired pastor. </div><div class="t m6b3 x73 h3f y5a9 ff4 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check at your local Adventist Book Center </div><div class="t mdb2 x73 h3f y3b2 ff4 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the companion book to the Sabbath </div><div class="t m86b x73 h3f y1582 ff4 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">School Lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
